Last Broadcast Date: Fri 20 Apr 2012
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world: today, the Argentine woman who went undercover in brothels to find her kidnapped daughter. From rag trade to rich list: one of Britain's most famous entrepreneurs James Caan talks about the price of success. He's just released a book called "Start your business in 7 days". And a Malian businesswoman on life since the coup. Show less